entries.journal_entry_description: Aid the Emperor in his plan to manipulate the Queen of Naboo into revealing the location of a Rebel General she is believed to be hiding.
entries.journal_entry_title: The Emperor and the Queen, Part II
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The mercenaries are going to try and intimidate the Queen and get her to reveal the location of a Rebel General she is hiding. To aid them, you will eliminate her security detail at the palace in Theed.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The Queen was not pleased with her visit from the mercenaries and has become quite vocal over this.  Lord Vader has informed her that the Empire had no involvement with this. Speak with her and convey the Emperor's assurances that she has the complete support of the Empire.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Emperor Palpatine at his retreat on Naboo.
